#  Automation Project: AI Powered CRM System

> Goal: This project automatate customer inquiries into a single sheet and auto fills the CRM with the client data/requirement, and then classifies the inquiry/generate lead and then automatically reply.  
> Tools: Zapier, Google Forms, Google Sheets, Gmail, OpenAI, HubSpot   
> Status: ðŸŸ¢ Working 
> Last Updated: 04-02-2026 

---

## 1) Overview

### What problem does this solve?
- This solves the problem of manually entering all customer data into your CRM/Sheet, and then drafting emails manually to send to each client.
- Who benefits: Team/service provider
- Better tracking, Fewer User input errors.

### Outcome (What it does)
When: Customer fills out the form, this automation will:
1. Fill up the CRM customer contact information.
2. Fill up attached sheet for database purposes.
3. Identify whether or not there is potential to get from client contact or not.
4. Optional: Notifications / logging. 

