---

### Step 5 â€” Split into Paths

- Create 3 Paths
- Classify each path
  - Path A - OpenAI : Category - if text contains (Cold Lead)
  - Path B - OpenAI : Category - if text contains (Warm Lead)
  - Path C - OpenAI : Category - If text contains (Hot Lead)

### Step 6 â€” Split into Paths
- Type: Action
- Event: Send Gmail - Send New Email
- Rules:
  - If Path A - OpenAI : Category - if text contains (Cold Lead) - Send new email with - Template for Cold Lead
  - IF Path B - OpenAI : Category - if text contains (Warm Lead) - Send new email with - Template for Warm Lead
  - IF Path C - OpenAI : Category - If text contains (Hot Lead)  - Send new email with - Template for Hot Lead
